text:
[Verse]
Under stars we dance all night
City lights fade out of sight
Wind it whispers soft and light
Hold me close till morning bright

[Verse 2]
Moonlight shadows on your face
Heartbeats sync in this embrace
Timeless moments time won't erase
Lost together in this space

[Chorus]
Starry night dreams come true
Here with you skies are blue
Whispered words just us two
Starry night me and you

[Verse 3]
Eyes that sparkle like the sky
Holding hands as worlds pass by
Endless stories you and I
In this night feels like we fly

[Bridge]
Never felt a love so right
In your eyes I see the light
Every star is shining bright
Forever starts tonight

[Chorus]
Starry night dreams come true
Here with you skies are blue
Whispered words just us two
Starry night me and you
title: Starry Night
